/div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ffac974dba799956a97d63ffcb13a774f700149c/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L381-L386","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delabFor","line":381,"kind":"opaque","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delabFor","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delabFor\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">delabFor</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ffac974dba799956a97d63ffcb13a774f700149c/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L371-L379","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.omission","line":371,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.omission","doc":"Delaborates the current expression as `⋯` and attaches `Elab.OmissionInfo`, which influences how the\nsubterm omitted by `⋯` is delaborated when hovered over.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.omission\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">omission</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(reason : <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason\">Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ffac974dba799956a97d63ffcb13a774f700149c/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L350-L369","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.shouldOmitProof","line":350,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.shouldOmitProof","doc":"Returns `true` if the given expression is a proof and should be omitted.\nThis function only returns `true` if `pp.proofs` is set to `false`.\n\n\"Shallow\" proofs are not omitted.\nThe `pp.proofs.threshold` option controls the depth threshold for what constitutes a shallow proof.\nSee `Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.isShallowExpression`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.shouldOmitProof\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">shouldOmitProof</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(e : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ffac974dba799956a97d63ffcb13a774f700149c/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L326-L348","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.shouldOmitExpr","line":326,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.shouldOmitExpr","doc":"Returns `true` if, at the current depth, we should omit the term and use `⋯` rather than\ndelaborating it. This function can only return `true` if `pp.deepTerms` is set to `false`.\nIt also contains a heuristic to allow \"shallow terms\" to be delaborated, even if they appear deep in\nan expression, which prevents terms such as atomic expressions or `OfNat.ofNat` literals from being\ndelaborated as `⋯`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.shouldOmitExpr\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">shouldOmitExpr</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(e : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ffac974dba799956a97d63ffcb13a774f700149c/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L313-L324","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.isShallowExpression","line":313,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.isShallowExpression","doc":"Returns true if `e` is a \"shallow\" expression.\nLocal variables, constants, and other atomic expressions are always shallow.\nIn general, an expression is considered to be shallow if its depth is at most `threshold`.\n\nSince the implementation uses `Lean.Expr.approxDepth`, the `threshold` is clamped to `[0, 254]`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.isShallowExpression\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">isShallowExpression</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(threshold : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(e : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ffac974dba799956a97d63ffcb13a774f700149c/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L305-L311","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withIncDepth","line":305,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withIncDepth","doc":"Runs the delaborator `act` with increased depth.\nThe depth is used when `pp.deepTerms` is `false` to determine what is a deep term.\nSee also `Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Context.depth`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withIncDepth\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">withIncDepth</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(act : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ffac974dba799956a97d63ffcb13a774f700149c/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L300-L303","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.addOmissionInfo.mkOmissionInfo","line":300,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.addOmissionInfo.mkOmissionInfo","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.addOmissionInfo.mkOmissionInfo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">addOmissionInfo</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkOmissionInfo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(reason : <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason\">Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(stx : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Lean.Syntax</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(e : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM</a> <a href=\"